zero                                  macro                                 zero

NAME
     zzeerroo - search for or set a motor's mechanical zero

SYNOPSIS

     zzeerroo mmoottoorr [[mmoottoorr ...... ]]

DESCRIPTION

     The zzeerroo macro is used to set the dial angles to zero for motors equipped
     with a home-position feature.  A search for the mechanical zero is
     undertaken when using the Microcontrole IP28.

EXAMPLE

     zzeerroo tthhee oommee pphhii ppssii

